{"tid":811590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新昌M+項目近300員工被炒","createTime":"2018-09-09T03:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T08:19:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fb84666843426de8e40f10eb927335cb5b9049f8","tid":811590,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:17:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180909/20495504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F20495504&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=59fb8b51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180909%2F20495504&h=6ccb909b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180909/20495504</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月09日 <br />\n<br />\n新昌M+項目近300員工被炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180909/large/a0504a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180909%2Flarge%2Fa0504a.gif&h=144cdb43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】西九管理局上月中突然宣佈，由於M+總承建商新昌營造瀕臨破產，因此局方即時解除與新昌約59億元合約。有參與M+項目的新昌員工向《蘋果》透露，近300名相關員工近日被裁，但新昌未有交代會否支付遣散費，又拖欠部份員工的8月份薪金，亦無供款予強積金戶口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未交代會否發遣散費<br />\n<br />\n參與M+工程的新昌監工陳先生（化名）指出，新昌的M+員工包括工程師及繪圖師等合共約300人，絕大部份上月底被新昌裁走，只留下少數員工「執手尾」。<br />\n<br />\n他向記者出示新昌發出的解僱信（圖），顯示僱傭關係將於9月底正式結束，公司會發放該時段的基本薪金及福利（basic remuneration and benefits package），但內文無提及遣散費。陳先生指，一眾員工曾向人事部了解遣散費問題，但未有正面回應，「我哋非常徬徨及無助」。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，以往公司是月尾出糧，但至今他仍未收到8月份的薪金。據他了解，至少30名同事亦被拖糧。陳先生翻查強積金戶口，發現公司由今年5月起已沒有供款，「公司嗰5%冇供，扣起我份糧嗰5%又冇供落去，咁啲錢去咗邊？」<br />\n<br />\n他指一眾同事將於日內到勞工處投訴。另外有新昌員工亦向記者指，他在8月尾才收到7月份的薪金，但坦言「都慣咗公司拖糧啦」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向新昌查詢，截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n范國威：收緊議規削監察職能"},{"pid":"777f6b8cf1fbf191711945156975d07aff77c10c","tid":811590,"uid":208074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"新昌呢間仆街公司"},{"pid":"63288b95c9e9282ffe1f3bc99bb1bbe142fb0b04","tid":811590,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976f157c58746086467b0ec672f1af2af479b499","tid":811590,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"70年歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ede2e53ca4733cf0a99fd4888c37647b21635cc","tid":811590,"uid":990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"工賊會又深潛了"},{"pid":"96ae648345e9205a537820c7933e80c0e95781f3","tid":811590,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"976f157c58746086467b0ec672f1af2af479b499","tid":811590,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"70年歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"200x年已經賣咗比大陸人"},{"pid":"a9543e665dd2805bcbecc6d3d1f1865f18481f77","tid":811590,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"其實資金有問題都成年有多，成行都知，唔明點解仲有人未走繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b9ac038de8d4a6500ac0d54d3f8ef7c75374cc","tid":811590,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9543e665dd2805bcbecc6d3d1f1865f18481f77","tid":811590,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"其實資金有問題都成年有多，成行都知，唔明點解仲有人未走繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g